[{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"CurrentModule = KhepriAutoCAD","category":"page"},{"location":"#KhepriAutoCAD","page":"Home","title":"KhepriAutoCAD","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"A Khepri backend for AutoCAD, communicating via a C# plugin over TCP (port 11000).","category":"page"},{"location":"#Architecture","page":"Home","title":"Architecture","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"KhepriAutoCAD is a SocketBackend using the :CS (C#) binary protocol. The Julia side sends geometry and material commands to a C# plugin running inside AutoCAD's process space.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Backend type: SocketBackend{ACADKey, Int64}\nReference IDs: Int64 (AutoCAD object handles)\nCoordinate system: Right-handed Z-up (no transforms needed)","category":"page"},{"location":"#Key-Features","page":"Home","title":"Key Features","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"190+ remote API calls: Full geometry, materials, layers, rendering, BIM, and annotation support\nDimension styles: Architectural (_ARCHTICK) and mechanical dimension formats\nMaterial system: Fine-grained control via AutoCADBasicMaterial with projection and tiling modes\nBIM elements: Walls, floors, doors, windows, tables, chairs\nLighting: Point lights, spotlights, IES photometric lights, and area lights (approximated as point lights)\nUser selection: Interactive pick of positions, points, curves, surfaces, and solids\nPlugin auto-update: Automatic deployment of C# plugin DLLs\nSHX fonts: Optional SHX text rendering via the use_shx parameter","category":"page"},{"location":"#Setup","page":"Home","title":"Setup","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"using KhepriAutoCAD\nusing KhepriBase\n\nbackend(autocad)\n\n# Geometry works through standard Khepri API\nsphere(xyz(0, 0, 0), 5)","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Requires AutoCAD with the Khepri C# plugin installed and listening on TCP port 11000.","category":"page"},{"location":"#Dependencies","page":"Home","title":"Dependencies","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"KhepriBase: Core Khepri functionality\nSockets: TCP communication","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Modules = [KhepriAutoCAD]","category":"page"}]
